txt.en: You have freed the dwarves who were about to become meals to some slavering Orcs in Uzbad-bakân.

Upon entering the kitchens of Uzbad-bakân, you happen upon struggling dwarf-captives. They have been captured by Orcs and dragged here...to be turned into dinner!\n\nYou should free the dwarf-captives of Uzbad-bakân before they can be eaten by the Orcs.
You have freed the dwarves who were about to become meals to some slavering Orcs in Uzbad-bakân.
You have discovered that several dwarves have been captured by Orcs and delivered to the kitchens of Uzbad-bakân...to be turned into dinner!
Free dwarf captives in the Uzbad-bakân kitchens
Dwarf-captives can be found in the kitchen area of Uzbad-bakân in southern Zelem-melek.\n\nYou should free dwarf-captives before the Orcs can cook them into dinner.
